videos.headline: Hurts uses legs for Oklahoma TD
videos.description: Jalen Hurts runs 55 yards to start the game for the Sooners, and finishes the drive with a 30-yard touchdown run.

videos.headline: Hurts goes off for big TD night vs. UCLA
videos.description: Jalen Hurts throws three touchdowns and runs in one himself, collecting 439 total yards.

videos.headline: Kelly on Hurts: 'I think he's a special player'
videos.description: Chip Kelly reflects on UCLA's loss to Oklahoma and calls Jalen Hurts one of the best quarterbacks he's coached against.
